  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This descriptive study aims to evalaute in a retrospective way the incidence of cogntive
      changes postoperatively after fast-track colon surgery at Hvidovre Hospital. This survey is
      based on chart reviews.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
